title: ArcGIS Registered Datastore
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: GPL
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors validation results for registered ArcGIS Server datastores.

 Registered datastores are external data locations registered with ArcGIS Server.
 The special agent validates each datastore through the Server admin API and
 reports success, warning, failure, error, unsupported, or unknown results.
item:
 The datastore path. If ArcGIS returns per-machine validation results, the item
 can include the machine name.
discovery:
 One service is discovered for each registered datastore validation result.
